= & \left(0-ax^{0}\right)+\left(0\right)+\left(0\right)+\left(0\right)+\cdots+\left(0\right)+\left(ax^{n+1}\right)\\
= & \left(-ax^{0}\right)+\left(ax^{n+1}\right)\\
